                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000b22d1afa-96e9-4371-8127-88e2b4c294ae" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({y=cot}^{-1}\ {\sqrt{\frac{2co{s}^{2}\frac{x}{2}\ }{2si{n}^{2}\frac{x}{2}}}}={cot}^{-1}\ {\sqrt{{cot}^{2}\ {\frac{x}{2}}}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b22d1afa-96e9-4371-8127-88e2b4c294ae"><sup> </sup></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b22d1afa-96e9-4371-8127-88e2b4c294ae {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b22d1afa-96e9-4371-8127-88e2b4c294ae {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000001767c51e-c34b-45f7-b46e-46ccb46ef447" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(={cot}^{-1}\ {\left(cot\ {\frac{x}{2}}\right)}=\frac{x}{2}\ ∴\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{1}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011767c51e-c34b-45f7-b46e-46ccb46ef447"><sup> </sup></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001767c51e-c34b-45f7-b46e-46ccb46ef447 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000011767c51e-c34b-45f7-b46e-46ccb46ef447 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
