                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000082152eb-98fe-4780-bf54-37f870246d39" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y={sin}^{2}\ {x+{cos}^{2}\ {x=1}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001082152eb-98fe-4780-bf54-37f870246d39"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000082152eb-98fe-4780-bf54-37f870246d39 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001082152eb-98fe-4780-bf54-37f870246d39 {font-family: Arial;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000060544717-80e7-4aea-8e27-88086f2cebd0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\frac{dy}{dx}=0;\ \frac{d}{dx}\left(ln{e}^{x}\right)=\frac{d}{dx}\left(x\right)=1\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000160544717-80e7-4aea-8e27-88086f2cebd0"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000060544717-80e7-4aea-8e27-88086f2cebd0 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000160544717-80e7-4aea-8e27-88086f2cebd0 {font-family: Arial;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
