                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000008499452c-b985-4810-b06b-37b3b4c5a54f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(s=3{t}^{3}-2t+4\ ;\ \frac{ds}{dt}=v=(9{t}^{2}-2){ms}^{-1}\ ;\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018499452c-b985-4810-b06b-37b3b4c5a54f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008499452c-b985-4810-b06b-37b3b4c5a54f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018499452c-b985-4810-b06b-37b3b4c5a54f {font-family: Arial;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000d57537d7-fa76-48ce-94fa-1a10ca3ad33e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{dv}{dt}=a=(18t-0){ms}^{-2}∴\frac{dv}{dt}{|}_{t=2}=36\ {ms}^{-2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d57537d7-fa76-48ce-94fa-1a10ca3ad33e"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d57537d7-fa76-48ce-94fa-1a10ca3ad33e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d57537d7-fa76-48ce-94fa-1a10ca3ad33e {font-family: Arial;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
