                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000007a4db04-fe82-4c2a-bf7b-de1491f27709" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(f\left(x\right)={x}^{2}+\frac{k}{x}⇒{f}^{{'}}\left(x\right)=2x-\frac{k}{{x}^{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000107a4db04-fe82-4c2a-bf7b-de1491f27709"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000007a4db04-fe82-4c2a-bf7b-de1491f27709 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000107a4db04-fe82-4c2a-bf7b-de1491f27709 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000988b8a47-b239-4fee-98ad-321b87774111" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴{f}^{{'}}\left(1\right)=2.1-\frac{k}{{1}^{2}\ }=2-k\ ;{f}^{{'}{'}}\left(x\right)=2+\frac{2k}{{x}^{3}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001988b8a47-b239-4fee-98ad-321b87774111"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000988b8a47-b239-4fee-98ad-321b87774111 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001988b8a47-b239-4fee-98ad-321b87774111 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cec3511e-9c9b-454f-8ab5-e79cf627580d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cec3511e-9c9b-454f-8ab5-e79cf627580d">Pig </span><span class="pt-000001cec3511e-9c9b-454f-8ab5-e79cf627580d">gv</span><span class="pt-000001cec3511e-9c9b-454f-8ab5-e79cf627580d">‡</span><span class="pt-000001cec3511e-9c9b-454f-8ab5-e79cf627580d">bi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cec3511e-9c9b-454f-8ab5-e79cf627580d"> Rb&#168;, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !importa