                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000be9c112c-cdf9-48eb-be9b-1f93e972f9cf" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y=x+\frac{1}{x}∴{y}_{1}=1-\frac{1}{{x}^{2}}∴{y}_{2}=\frac{2}{{x}^{3}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001be9c112c-cdf9-48eb-be9b-1f93e972f9cf"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000be9c112c-cdf9-48eb-be9b-1f93e972f9cf {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001be9c112c-cdf9-48eb-be9b-1f93e972f9cf {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007a58b4d8-1311-47ad-9d54-5c987b50323f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000017a58b4d8-1311-47ad-9d54-5c987b50323f">GLb</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017a58b4d8-1311-47ad-9d54-5c987b50323f">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({y}_{1}=0⇒1-\frac{1}{{x}^{2}}=0⇒{x}^{2}=1⇒x=\ ±1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000027a58b4d8-1311-47ad-9d54-5c987b50323f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007a58b4d8-1311-47ad-9d54-5c987b50323f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017a58b4d8-1311-47ad-9d54-5c987b50323f {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000027a58b4d8-1311-47ad-9d54-5c987b50323f {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007e67f0b3-e5d4-4215-b45d-3f6fc4353930" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=\ 1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017e67f0b3-e5d4-4215-b45d-3f6fc4353930"> n‡j, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family