                                            <p class="pt-0000005023d2a3-4827-410e-bdd4-b71bcd72bf85" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sin\ {y}=\frac{2t}{1+{t}^{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000015023d2a3-4827-410e-bdd4-b71bcd72bf85"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000025023d2a3-4827-410e-bdd4-b71bcd72bf85">I </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sec\ {x}=\frac{1+{t}^{2}}{1-{t}^{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000025023d2a3-4827-410e-bdd4-b71bcd72bf85"> n‡j, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{dy}{dx}=?\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005023d2a3-4827-410e-bdd4-b71bcd72bf85 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000015023d2a3-4827-410e-bdd4-b71bcd72bf85 {font-family: Arial;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000025023d2a3-4827-410e-bdd4-b71bcd72bf85 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
